Alternatively, GraphicsGale lets you rearrange colors in the palette. Make sure to hold down Shift while dragging colors so the pixels remain the same color (i.e. the image is adapted to the new palette).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4526">Sik</a> — Fri Sep 26, 2014 5:11 pm</p><hr />
